Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:23.53,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,80)}#20  我們全員相會於天城屋旅館
Comment: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭的所有活動都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.54,0:02:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請各位執行委員到放映室集合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼  結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  那接下來要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃點東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個主意好  JUNES王子請客
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.16,0:02:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  讓兩位選美冠軍請客怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然想讓女孩子請客  真是過分啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要擊穿你的心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別自稱女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.49,0:02:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…請不要再提大賽的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們就這麼解散的話也太沒意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:02:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜菜子  原來你來參觀文化祭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我吃過炒麵了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還跳了舞  玩了鬼屋  還去占卜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去占卜過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  一個漂亮的姐姐說哥哥是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  小…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說我是小…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小白臉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說你是天生的小白臉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們找過你了  但總是碰不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一大早我就要出差去縣廳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜我就得動身了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你和菜菜子看家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  學長要回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜菜子一個人也能看家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:03:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  菜菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜菜子真是個乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那菜菜子今晚要不要住我家的店裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和哥哥一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？哎！小雪你剛才說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問她要不要住我家的店裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在旅館開個慶祝會？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  但是  菜菜子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  太棒啊  住旅館啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是請菜菜子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吃得到溫泉雞蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是住一晚吧  那我得先和爺爺說一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫泉  浴衣  盛開的鮮花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是直斗  爺爺在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是去幹壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住旅館嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都會來  很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎  來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要住旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  大家在家裡準備好之後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就集體在天城屋旅館集合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然還是先回一趟家再出門…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛西小姐  要給您添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這麼多人真是不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢  我們久候各位多時了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  小雪是溫泉旅館未來的老闆娘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  我只是個女服務員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊  突然來了一群團體客
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪  難得有朋友來  你明明可以全都交給我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宴會結束之前還需要人手對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我來領各位去房間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  拜託…了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛佳？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  打工
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我沒說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她時不時會過來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時不時來幫忙的話  愛家那邊怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒問題的  請到房間去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色調是不是有些太鮮豔了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可能淺一些  能讓人放鬆的那種比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得學姐好帥氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花的數量也稍微減少些…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.11,0:05:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過大家沒住同一個房間啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在隔壁的話我就忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她們的房間也離得太遠了熊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼空房了  所以女生的房間好像在另一層
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好無聊啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這半年來我們還真是經常在一起過夜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帳篷  酒店  還有旅館嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服換的真快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好飽好飽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃得好滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請好好享受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好幸福啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼接下來要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打撲克嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.65,0:06:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生們說要去泡溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是混浴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:06:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:06:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不喜歡泡好多次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡前去泡一下就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來這個房間…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是挺高檔的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你也很在意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說旺季中這種房間怎麼可能會空呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是故意裝作不知道罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡說不定發生過什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大家為什麼都一聲不吭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完…完二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去接接看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長們害怕個什麼勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.18,0:07:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去接
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是嗎  多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露天浴場現在好像沒什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了一身汗真不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就去洗個澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和大家一起洗澡  真讓人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:27.73,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(105,350)\3c88B4E7\bord6\fsp1}熊熊的想像畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:27.73,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(105,350)\3c1E3B8E\bord3\fsp1}熊熊的想像畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家坐向同一個方向互相擦背
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者會邊看富士山邊唱歌對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的世界充滿了開心的事情啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也都多虧了老師啊  謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  電梯到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(223,42)\fs20\1c202A42\bord0\shad0\b1}露天浴場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,42)\fs20\1c202A42\bord0\shad0\b1}大浴場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直斗同學  過來吧  這邊地方很大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直斗的皮膚真光滑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊  摸上去滑溜溜的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  皮膚又白頭髮又柔順
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在摸什麼地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你像這樣住在外面沒問題嗎  不害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為平時在哥哥回家前  我一直都是一個人看家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很會看家的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人在家的話碰到陌生人敲門不能開門
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些道理我是明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  你真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說菜菜子  要不要試著游游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從小就一直在游
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也會在這裡游泳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快否定啊  雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們來比誰先游到那邊的水潭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸掉的人要請客喝水果牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想喝彈珠汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我也要參加嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要參加嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備  開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這浴場真大啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我一展身手來個熊扒式吧熊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:09:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為為為什麼你們會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我們的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠…悠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況糟糕透頂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請快點出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直斗  嗚哇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候就要鼓起勇氣  留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這種勇氣究竟有什麼意義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們撤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色狼行為可是違法的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了這是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們給我記住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下可得好好教訓教訓他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害  打中了好多下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐我很準對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有沒有被看到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡在這個時間段是供男性使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄錯時間了  啊哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說什麼「啊哈哈」  不是吧
